Package com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support.managers.packages

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Versions
    The Versions interface provides methods to inspect a Hardware Support Package (HSP)'s detailed information.
    VersionsTypes
    The Versions interface provides methods to inspect a Hardware Support Package (HSP)'s detailed information.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PackagesFactory
    PackagesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support.managers.packages package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.

    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.esx.settings.hardware_support.managers.packages package.

    VersionsTypes.ComponentInfo
